<h1 style="font-size:300%">Stan</h1>
<hr />

<!--
<img style="float: left" src="stanlogo-main.png"/> 
-->

<p> Stan is a package for obtaining Bayesian inference using the
No-U-Turn sampler, a variant of Hamiltonian Monte Carlo.</p>

